    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Frustrated with their poor user experience, I promptly reminded myself that ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Canva",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " offers their own video editing tools.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://www.canva.com/"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "That’s where I discovered this fun animation—which shows up during the process of uploading media (images, videos) to your project.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "//s.imgur.com/min/embed.js",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "//s.imgur.com/min/embed.js"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "I couldn’t help but notice the sharp contrast between this “affordance,” and the one used by Wave to indicate the status of videos being rendered. (Hint: it just shows a percentage.)",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Of course, it’s not the animation itself that makes it effective. What makes it effective is that it’s a ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "reliable",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " indicator of the system status.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "If it were constantly run for several minutes, it wouldn’t be effective. It would be annoying.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "If it plummeted from 89% back to 62%, it would be frustrating.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Point is, you can’t merely communicate that the user is ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "almost there.",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " You have to take steps to ensure they’re actually waiting ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "for",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " something.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Otherwise, you’re just wasting their time.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}